name: svelte-tags-search-input
description: Create customizable Svelte components for tag input and search.
readme:
svelte-tags-search-input

## Introduction It's based on [svelte-tags-input](https://github.com/agustinl/svelte-tags-input).It can return extra string that hasn't transformed into a value of tags by ```js bind:extra = {...}; ``` It's just retrofitted for [cute_web](https://github.com/nyansite/cute_web) . ## Install ```javascript import Tags from "svelte-tags-search-input"; ``` ## License This project is open source and available under the [MIT License](LICENSE). ## Author [@agustinl](https://twitter.com/agustinlautaro) [@flyingsnoopy](https://github.com/flyingsnoopy) ##### 2023
